The eaiset way is:

1. Burn the new version of Tails on a DVD and boot from it.
2. Insert (but don't mount) the USB stick containing the old Tails installation.
3. Start **Applications -> Tails -> Tails USB installer**.
4. Select **Clone & Upgrade**.
5. Select the correct USB device and install.

